Preconditions:
The input grid must not be null.
The input grid must have at least one row and one column.
The row and col parameters must be within the bounds of the input grid.
The color parameter must be a valid integer value.

Postconditions:
The final grid returned must have the same dimensions as the input grid.
The cell at the specified row and col in the final grid must have the color specified.
The border cells of the final grid must have their color changed if they are adjacent to cells with a different color.
All other cells in the final grid must remain unchanged.